N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4022.17 - Disqualification of horses

State Regulations

No horse that is disqualified or ineligible, as
provided in this Subchapter, or nominated by, or the property, wholly or in
part, of a person who is unlicensed, disqualified or ineligible, as provided in
this Subchapter, may be entered or started in a race. Notes
